chapter.para:
The Tracker Business Intelligence Toolkit and Features
	consists of the following types of task specific utilities and tools:



Data Importing Utilities;




Data Exporting Utilities;




Tools for Querying Operational Data;



Utilities for interfacing with Tag Id Readers, including support for 
					serial and Bluetooth connections;




Utilities for interfacing with network attached sensors;




Utilities for interfacing with industry standard Geography Information Systems GIS and geobrowsers;




Eclipse Business Intelligence Reporting Tools BIRT.
